      "content": "The `generate_token` function in `auth_service.py` returns a byte string when using `jwt.encode`, but `jwt.decode` expects the token to be a string. You need to decode the output of `generate_token` before passing it to `validate_token`. Simply changing the return line in `generate_token` to `return jwt.encode(payload, SECRET_KEY, algorithm='HS256').decode('utf-8')` will make the test pass instantly.",
